<TEXT>
A FIRE yesterday destroyed one of the most eye-catching pavilions of the
Seville Universal Exposition, which opens on April 20, writes Tom Burns in
Madrid.
Firemen fought a four-hour battle to extinguish the blaze at the 'Time
Machine'. Conceived as a Time Machine that used a combination of visual
